quran[10]{c,v,t,f}:
  28,85,"Dájúdájú Ẹni tí Ó ṣe al-Ƙur’ān ní ọ̀ran-anyàn fún ọ (láti mú un lò àti láti pèpè sí i), Ó sì máa dá ọ padà sí ibùpadàsí kan (nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra). Sọ pé: “Olúwa mi nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ẹni tí ó mú ìmọ̀nà wá àti ta ni ó wà nínú ìṣìnà pọ́nńbélé.”",""
  28,86,"Ìwọ kò sì retí pé A óò sọ tírà al-Ƙur’ān kalẹ̀ fún ọ (tẹ́lẹ̀), àmọ́ ó jẹ́ ìkẹ́ kan láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ. Nítorí náà, o ò gbọdọ̀ jẹ́ olùrànlọ́wọ́ fún àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́.",""
  28,87,"Má ṣe jẹ́ kí wọ́n ṣẹ́ ọ lórí kúrò níbi àwọn āyah Allāhu lẹ́yìn ìgbà tí A ti sọ̀ ọ́ kalẹ̀ fún ọ. Pèpè sí ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ. Ìwọ kò sì gbọ́dọ̀ wà nínú àwọn ọ̀ṣẹbọ.",""
  28,88,"Má ṣe pe ọlọ́hun mìíràn mọ́ Allāhu. Kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí ẹ gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Òun. Gbogbo n̄ǹkan l’ó máa parun àfi Ojú Rẹ̀ (ìyẹn pàápàá bíbẹ Allāhu -subhānu wa ta‘ālā -). TiRẹ̀ ni ìdájọ́. Ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ sì ni wọn yóò da yín padà sí.",""
  29,1,"’Alif lām mīm. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1."
  29,2,"Ǹjẹ́ àwọn ènìyàn lérò pé A óò fi wọ́n sílẹ̀ kí wọ́n máa sọ pé: “A gbàgbọ́”, tí A ò sì níí dán wọn wò?",""
  29,3,"A kúkú ti dán àwọn tó ṣíwájú wọn wò. Nítorí náà, dájúdájú Allāhu máa ṣàfi hàn àwọn tó sọ òdodo. Dájúdájú Ó sì máa ṣàfi hàn àwọn òpùrọ́.",""
  29,4,"Àbí àwọn tó ń ṣe iṣẹ́ aburú lérò pé àwọn máa mórí bọ́ mọ́ Wa lọ́wọ́ ni? Ohun tí wọ́n ń dá lẹ́jọ́ burú.",""
  29,5,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá ń retí ìpàdé Allāhu, dájúdájú àkókò Allāhu kúkú ń bọ̀. Òun sì ni Olùgbọ́, Onímọ̀.",""
  29,6,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá gbìyànjú, ó ń gbìyànjú fún ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀ ni. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Ọlọ́rọ̀ tí kò bùkátà sí gbogbo ẹ̀dá.",""
